desc: Don's Disc Golf has been operating as a Disc Golf retailer in Calgary Alberta Canada since 2012. We have a flat shipping rate in Canada of $9.00 with Free Shipping on orders over $65.00. Discs, Bags, Hats, Practice Baskets, Apparel, Glow Discs, Beginner Starter Sets, Custom Dyed Discs and so much more!
